<div class="block outer online-course-wrapper w-100 hb ha">
    <div class="block inner online-course w-100 hb ha">
        <div class="block text-content hb ha">
            <div class="block heading hb ha">
                <h2>Class B Theory Online Course</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="block info hb ha">
                <p>Our online Class B Theory course covers all requirements to comply with the Entry Level Driving Training (ELDT) mandate. C1 Truck Driver Training is registered with the FMCSA Training Provider Registry (TPR) list of approved schools.</p>
                <p>The Class B Theory Online Course covers all of the basic information that is required per FMCSA guidelines. Each unit provides study questions upon completion to help students retain information throughout the course. Upon completing all units, a proficiency exam will be administered with a required passing score of 80% or higher. The exam can be taken as many times as needed until the student receives a passing grade and results can successfully be submitted to the Training Provider Registry.</p>
